  "description": "Depth subscription flow — 20-level (49 instruments per NIFTY/BANKNIFTY) and 200-level (ATM CE + PE for NIFTY/BANKNIFTY only). FINNIFTY + MIDCPNIFTY were dropped 2026-04-25 to free 25K WS capacity for stock F&O ATM±25. Red panels indicate depth connection failures, rebalancer stalls, or dropped frames. Runbook: .claude/rules/project/depth-subscription.md.",
  "editable": true,
